such
a
risk.
But
against
this
there
were
objections;
and
she
finally
resolved
that
it
could
be
the
last
resource,
if
her
private
inquiries
to
the
absence
of
the
family
were
unfavourably
answered.
Accordingly,
when
she
retired
at
night,
she
asked
the
chambermaid
whether
Pemberley
were
not
a
very
fine
place?
what
was
the
name
of
its
proprietor?
and,
with
no
