whether
the
family
were
down
for
the
summer?
A
most
welcome
negative
followed
the
last
question
and
her
alarms
now
being
removed,
she
was
at
leisure
to
feel
a
great
deal
of
curiosity
to
see
the
house
herself;
and
when
the
